autonomous in making decisions?

57:22.000 --> 57:24.000
Do I give her feedback?

57:24.000 --> 57:26.000
Does she receive it?

57:26.000 --> 57:28.000
Do I pay attention

57:28.000 --> 57:30.000
to my employee?

57:30.000 --> 57:32.000
How well or badly he works?

57:32.000 --> 57:34.000
Do I tell him about it?

