for any financial investments.

58:04.000 --> 58:06.000
That is, we increase the motivation

58:06.000 --> 58:08.000
of our employees just by saying a word,

58:08.000 --> 58:10.000
just by changing their attitude,

58:10.000 --> 58:12.000
just by paying attention to them.

58:12.000 --> 58:14.000
Accordingly, people will start

58:14.000 --> 58:16.000
working more effectively,

58:16.000 --> 58:18.000
and again, we will achieve our goals.

58:26.000 --> 58:28.000
Another thing I would like to say

58:28.000 --> 58:30.000
in terms of motivation is that

58:30.000 --> 58:32.000
each employee, different employees,

58:32.000 --> 58:34.000
let's say, have different types of motivation.

58:34.000 --> 58:36.000
That is, people are motivated

58:36.000 --> 58:38.000
by different things.

58:38.000 --> 58:40.000
One of the types

58:40.000 --> 58:42.000
is instrumental type.

58:42.000 --> 58:44.000
What is it?

58:44.000 --> 58:46.000
These are people who are very

58:46.000 --> 58:48.000
influenced by external stimuli.

58:48.000 --> 58:50.000
That is, they need to be constantly

58:50.000 --> 58:52.000
fed from the outside.

58:52.000 --> 58:54.000
Roughly speaking,

58:54.000 --> 58:56.000
not in vain we have a picture

58:56.000 --> 58:58.000
on the slide of money.

58:58.000 --> 59:00.000
This is a bonus,

59:00.000 --> 59:02.000
this is some social benefits,

59:02.000 --> 59:04.000
or a social program,

59:04.000 --> 59:06.000
this is an increase in social benefits,

59:06.000 --> 59:08.000
this is some possible trips,

59:08.000 --> 59:10.000
this is participation in some

59:10.000 --> 59:12.000
giving out of subscribers,

59:12.000 --> 59:14.000
perhaps.

59:14.000 --> 59:16.000
That is, these are the things

59:16.000 --> 59:18.000
that we can measure, give.

59:18.000 --> 59:20.000
That is, we can give that person

59:20.000 --> 59:22.000
physically, somewhere he can joke,

59:22.000 --> 59:24.000
feel, can go somewhere,

59:24.000 --> 59:26.000
enjoy.

59:26.000 --> 59:28.000
This is an instrumental type.

59:28.000 --> 59:30.000
What will such people talk about?

59:30.000 --> 59:32.000
That is, how can we identify it?

59:32.000 --> 59:34.000
These people will,

59:34.000 --> 59:36.000
as a rule,

59:36.000 --> 59:38.000
ask

59:38.000 --> 59:40.000
when setting the task,

59:40.000 --> 59:42.000
what will we get for it?

59:42.000 --> 59:44.000
Will we get an additional bonus?

59:44.000 --> 59:46.000
What will I get for it?

59:46.000 --> 59:48.000
All conversations will go

59:48.000 --> 59:50.000
around this.

59:50.000 --> 59:52.000
They will not be interested in the content of the work.

59:52.000 --> 59:54.000
What do I need to do for this?

59:54.000 --> 59:56.000
They have the first question, what will I get for it?

59:56.000 --> 59:58.000
The next type of motivation

59:58.000 --> 01:00:00.000
is a professional type.

01:00:00.000 --> 01:00:02.000
These are very interesting

01:00:02.000 --> 01:00:04.000
people, of course.

01:00:04.000 --> 01:00:06.000
These are people who are motivated

01:00:06.000 --> 01:00:08.000
by the work itself.

01:00:08.000 --> 01:00:10.000
The very content.

01:00:10.000 --> 01:00:12.000
People like to grow.

01:00:12.000 --> 01:00:14.000
People like to grow professionally.

01:00:14.000 --> 01:00:16.000
They need less

01:00:16.000 --> 01:00:18.000
some external stimuli.

01:00:18.000 --> 01:00:20.000
They just need to be given

01:00:20.000 --> 01:00:22.000
more work

01:00:22.000 --> 01:00:24.000
where they can develop themselves.

01:00:24.000 --> 01:00:26.000
That is, to expand their circle

01:00:26.000 --> 01:00:28.000
of duties. They did

01:00:28.000 --> 01:00:30.000
one job, then they did another.

01:00:30.000 --> 01:00:32.000
Accordingly, they expand.

01:00:32.000 --> 01:00:34.000
They grow.

01:00:34.000 --> 01:00:36.000
This is a professional type.

01:00:36.000 --> 01:00:38.000
What are these people motivated by?

01:00:38.000 --> 01:00:40.000
They like mentorship.

01:00:40.000 --> 01:00:42.000
They like to learn, they like to share

01:00:42.000 --> 01:00:44.000
their experience, they like to learn

01:00:44.000 --> 01:00:46.000
something new, they like to dig

01:00:46.000 --> 01:00:48.000
and improve their

01:00:48.000 --> 01:00:50.000
process of work.

01:00:50.000 --> 01:00:52.000
People are usually directed

01:00:52.000 --> 01:00:54.000
to the process.

01:00:54.000 --> 01:00:56.000
The next type of motivation is patriotic.

01:00:56.000 --> 01:00:58.000
These are people who are more

01:00:58.000 --> 01:01:00.000
directed to the team,

01:01:00.000 --> 01:01:02.000
to achieve some high ambitious

01:01:02.000 --> 01:01:04.000
goals.

01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:06.000
We are here, we are

01:01:06.000 --> 01:01:08.000
involved in such results.

01:01:08.000 --> 01:01:10.000
It's like with flags.

01:01:10.000 --> 01:01:12.000
Forward!

01:01:12.000 --> 01:01:14.000
Forward, you give communism!

01:01:14.000 --> 01:01:16.000
Mission, vision, the leadership

01:01:16.000 --> 01:01:18.000
came down to us, wow!

01:01:18.000 --> 01:01:20.000
They are already very pleased.

01:01:20.000 --> 01:01:22.000
These are people who can ask for advice

01:01:22.000 --> 01:01:24.000
and they will always give it too.

01:01:24.000 --> 01:01:26.000
With great pleasure.

01:01:26.000 --> 01:01:28.000
They will be very motivated.

01:01:28.000 --> 01:01:30.000
These are the awards,

01:01:30.000 --> 01:01:32.000
the honours,

01:01:32.000 --> 01:01:34.000
all that people with a patriotic

01:01:34.000 --> 01:01:36.000
type like.

01:01:36.000 --> 01:01:38.000
The next type of motivation,

01:01:38.000 --> 01:01:40.000
you can't even call it a type of motivation

01:01:40.000 --> 01:01:42.000
because these people,

01:01:42.000 --> 01:01:44.000
let's say, don't really motivate.

01:01:44.000 --> 01:01:46.000
They are Lumpenized.

01:01:46.000 --> 01:01:48.000
Do you remember

01:01:48.000 --> 01:01:50.000
the expression Proletariat Lumpen?

