why me, why not Vasya,

01:02:06.000 --> 01:02:08.000
Petya or Fedya?

01:02:08.000 --> 01:02:10.000
These are people who

01:02:10.000 --> 01:02:12.000
don't like to show off

01:02:12.000 --> 01:02:14.000
and also don't like to be equal.

01:02:14.000 --> 01:02:16.000
Everyone is the same, everyone is equal.

01:02:16.000 --> 01:02:18.000
This is the type of people.

01:02:18.000 --> 01:02:20.000
Unfortunately,

01:02:20.000 --> 01:02:22.000
there are a lot of them.

01:02:22.000 --> 01:02:24.000
In my opinion, these people can still

01:02:24.000 --> 01:02:26.000
be moved somewhere,

01:02:26.000 --> 01:02:28.000
you can shake them somewhere

01:02:28.000 --> 01:02:30.000
and transfer them to something else,

01:02:30.000 --> 01:02:32.000
that is, to feel the button.

01:02:32.000 --> 01:02:34.000
But again, these are conversations,

01:02:34.000 --> 01:02:36.000
these are manifestations of needs.

01:02:36.000 --> 01:02:38.000
Accordingly, then we will understand

01:02:38.000 --> 01:02:40.000
what to do with this person.

01:02:40.000 --> 01:02:42.000
In life, there is no

01:02:42.000 --> 01:02:44.000
pure economic,

01:02:44.000 --> 01:02:46.000
pure patriotic type of motivation,

01:02:46.000 --> 01:02:48.000
pure professional,

01:02:48.000 --> 01:02:50.000
and so on.

01:02:50.000 --> 01:02:52.000
Naturally, these types will be mixed.

01:02:52.000 --> 01:02:54.000
I think that one person

01:02:54.000 --> 01:02:56.000
will be clearly expressed.

