The same is true of the host or the patriotic.

01:03:10.000 --> 01:03:12.000
The host and the patriotic

01:03:12.000 --> 01:03:14.000
very often happen together.

01:03:14.000 --> 01:03:16.000
That is, it is a joint achievement of goals.

