It is a charismatic leader,

01:41:06.000 --> 01:41:08.000
as they usually say.

01:41:08.000 --> 01:41:10.000
A charismatic leader who wants to follow.

01:41:10.000 --> 01:41:12.000
But it is very difficult

01:41:12.000 --> 01:41:14.000
to give leadership

01:41:14.000 --> 01:41:16.000
a definition, to drive it into the framework.

01:41:16.000 --> 01:41:18.000
Because sometimes

01:41:18.000 --> 01:41:20.000
a person is very charming

01:41:20.000 --> 01:41:22.000
and you want to follow him too.

01:41:22.000 --> 01:41:24.000
But he does not have such a loud voice,

01:41:24.000 --> 01:41:26.000
some bright charisma.

01:41:26.000 --> 01:41:28.000
But you also want to follow him,

01:41:28.000 --> 01:41:30.000
you listen to him.

01:41:30.000 --> 01:41:32.000
I would like to put

01:41:32.000 --> 01:41:34.000
not a dilemma,

01:41:34.000 --> 01:41:36.000
but a manager as an administrator

01:41:36.000 --> 01:41:38.000
and a manager as a leader.

01:41:38.000 --> 01:41:40.000
A manager administers,

01:41:40.000 --> 01:41:42.000
and a leader is engaged in innovations.

01:41:42.000 --> 01:41:44.000
That is, the leader is always looking ahead.

01:41:44.000 --> 01:41:46.000
A manager

01:41:46.000 --> 01:41:48.000
supports more,

01:41:48.000 --> 01:41:50.000
and a leader develops.

01:41:50.000 --> 01:41:52.000
That is, the administrator supported the employee somewhere,

01:41:52.000 --> 01:41:54.000
and the leader constantly develops.

01:41:54.000 --> 01:41:56.000
He shows

01:41:56.000 --> 01:41:58.000
positive moments,

01:41:58.000 --> 01:42:00.000
where there is a growth zone

01:42:00.000 --> 01:42:02.000
of our employee.

01:42:02.000 --> 01:42:04.000
An administrator or a manager

01:42:04.000 --> 01:42:06.000
is more of a builder,

01:42:06.000 --> 01:42:08.000
and a leader is an architect.

01:42:08.000 --> 01:42:10.000
A builder is the one who performs,

01:42:10.000 --> 01:42:12.000
and an architect is the one who invents

01:42:12.000 --> 01:42:14.000
what needs to be built.

01:42:14.000 --> 01:42:16.000
A manager accepts reality

01:42:16.000 --> 01:42:18.000
as it is, because he has

01:42:18.000 --> 01:42:20.000
a clearly set task in the Smart format,

01:42:20.000 --> 01:42:22.000
and he cannot go somewhere to the left or to the right.

01:42:22.000 --> 01:42:24.000
A leader

01:42:24.000 --> 01:42:26.000
changes reality more.

01:42:26.000 --> 01:42:28.000
He looks at how to make it better,

01:42:28.000 --> 01:42:30.000
and he changes the whole process

01:42:30.000 --> 01:42:32.000
to achieve the goal

01:42:32.000 --> 01:42:34.000
more effectively.

01:42:34.000 --> 01:42:36.000
A manager or an administrator

01:42:36.000 --> 01:42:38.000
relies more on control,

01:42:38.000 --> 01:42:40.000
and a leader trusts the employees.

01:42:40.000 --> 01:42:42.000
They do it on their own.

01:42:42.000 --> 01:42:44.000
A manager has a short-term view,

01:42:44.000 --> 01:42:46.000
and a leader sees

01:42:46.000 --> 01:42:48.000
the future.

01:42:48.000 --> 01:42:50.000
A manager asks how and when,

01:42:50.000 --> 01:42:52.000
and a leader asks what

01:42:52.000 --> 01:42:54.000
and why.

01:42:54.000 --> 01:42:56.000
A manager gives time to the details,

01:42:56.000 --> 01:42:58.000
and a leader looks at the horizon.

01:43:00.000 --> 01:43:02.000
To sum up,

01:43:02.000 --> 01:43:04.000
a manager does things right,

01:43:04.000 --> 01:43:06.000
and a leader does

01:43:06.000 --> 01:43:08.000
the right things.

01:43:12.000 --> 01:43:14.000
If we put a dilemma

01:43:14.000 --> 01:43:16.000
or a weight cup,

01:43:16.000 --> 01:43:18.000
what is more important

01:43:18.000 --> 01:43:20.000
to me as a manager

01:43:20.000 --> 01:43:22.000
to focus more on?

01:43:22.000 --> 01:43:24.000
To achieve high profits?

01:43:24.000 --> 01:43:26.000
What is more important?

01:43:26.000 --> 01:43:28.000
This or high profits?

01:43:28.000 --> 01:43:30.000
What is more important?

01:43:30.000 --> 01:43:32.000
According to the research,

01:43:32.000 --> 01:43:34.000
it is very important

01:43:34.000 --> 01:43:36.000
to do both.

01:43:36.000 --> 01:43:38.000
It is not a choice between

01:43:38.000 --> 01:43:40.000
both.

01:43:40.000 --> 01:43:42.000
You have to do both

01:43:42.000 --> 01:43:44.000
in equal proportions.

01:43:44.000 --> 01:43:46.000
You have to devote

01:43:46.000 --> 01:43:48.000
as much time as possible

01:43:48.000 --> 01:43:50.000
to high profits.

01:43:50.000 --> 01:43:52.000
It is about

01:43:52.000 --> 01:43:54.000
caring for clients

01:43:54.000 --> 01:43:56.000
who bring money

01:43:56.000 --> 01:43:58.000
to our company.

01:43:58.000 --> 01:44:00.000
It is about caring for employees.

01:44:00.000 --> 01:44:02.000
The more satisfied

01:44:02.000 --> 01:44:04.000
our employees are,

01:44:04.000 --> 01:44:06.000
the more satisfied our clients are.

01:44:06.000 --> 01:44:08.000
Accordingly, we will get profits.

01:44:08.000 --> 01:44:10.000
It is about focusing on tasks,

01:44:10.000 --> 01:44:12.000
goals,

01:44:12.000 --> 01:44:14.000
papers, standards,

01:44:14.000 --> 01:44:16.000
and focusing on people.

01:44:16.000 --> 01:44:18.000
Because people are behind

01:44:18.000 --> 01:44:20.000
these tasks.

01:44:20.000 --> 01:44:22.000
People are doing these tasks.

01:44:22.000 --> 01:44:24.000
It is about business development,

01:44:24.000 --> 01:44:26.000
investing money in innovation,

01:44:26.000 --> 01:44:28.000
in business, in development.

01:44:28.000 --> 01:44:30.000
It is about

01:44:30.000 --> 01:44:32.000
investing financial resources

01:44:32.000 --> 01:44:34.000
in people's development.

01:44:34.000 --> 01:44:36.000
It is important to do both.

01:44:36.000 --> 01:44:38.000
It is very difficult to choose.

01:44:38.000 --> 01:44:40.000
We cannot choose if we want to be effective

01:44:40.000 --> 01:44:42.000
and if we want our company

01:44:42.000 --> 01:44:44.000
to develop and work further.

01:44:44.000 --> 01:44:46.000
It is about toughness.

01:44:46.000 --> 01:44:48.000
Sometimes you need to demand

01:44:48.000 --> 01:44:50.000
toughness, clarity,

01:44:50.000 --> 01:44:52.000
and reason from your employees.

01:44:52.000 --> 01:44:54.000
It is about delicacy.

01:44:54.000 --> 01:44:56.000
When a person

01:44:56.000 --> 01:44:58.000
has not fulfilled his task,

01:44:58.000 --> 01:45:00.000
we have already discussed it,

01:45:00.000 --> 01:45:02.000
when we give feedback.

01:45:02.000 --> 01:45:04.000
It is about demanding,

01:45:04.000 --> 01:45:06.000
supporting,

01:45:06.000 --> 01:45:08.000
money,

01:45:08.000 --> 01:45:10.000
and entertainment.

01:45:10.000 --> 01:45:12.000
It is about hard work and hard play.

01:45:12.000 --> 01:45:14.000
How to make it so

01:45:14.000 --> 01:45:16.000
that you will not work

01:45:16.000 --> 01:45:18.000
for a day.

01:45:18.000 --> 01:45:20.000
It is about

01:45:20.000 --> 01:45:22.000
how to turn hard work

01:45:22.000 --> 01:45:24.000
into hard play

01:45:24.000 --> 01:45:26.000
so that everyone

01:45:26.000 --> 01:45:28.000
enjoys it.

01:45:28.000 --> 01:45:30.000
It is about

01:45:30.000 --> 01:45:32.000
financial reward

01:45:32.000 --> 01:45:34.000
that is expressed

01:45:34.000 --> 01:45:36.000
in all material stimuli.

01:45:36.000 --> 01:45:38.000
It is about moral reward

01:45:38.000 --> 01:45:40.000
that our employees need.

01:45:40.000 --> 01:45:42.000
It is about a manager

01:45:42.000 --> 01:45:44.000
and a person.

01:45:46.000 --> 01:45:48.000
It is about treating people

01:45:48.000 --> 01:45:50.000
as employees

01:45:50.000 --> 01:45:52.000
according to their functions,

01:45:52.000 --> 01:45:54.000
duties, rules,

01:45:54.000 --> 01:45:56.000
and treating them

01:45:56.000 --> 01:45:58.000
as individuals.

01:45:58.000 --> 01:46:00.000
It is about making decisions

01:46:00.000 --> 01:46:02.000
with your head

01:46:02.000 --> 01:46:04.000
and heart.

01:46:04.000 --> 01:46:06.000
It is about informing

01:46:06.000 --> 01:46:08.000
and listening.

